---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Best Shopify Email Apps for Gift Cards in 2026';
const description = 'Compare Shopify email apps for gift-card marketing by gifting intent, delivery, redemption, segmentation, pricing context, sources, and tradeoffs.';
const apps = [
['Sequenzy','Lean stores with simple gift-card sequences','Focused gifting and redemption workflows','Validate gift-card event support','https://sequenzy.com','Start with delivery instructions, a redemption reminder, and a post-redemption thank-you. Keep purchaser and recipient roles separate and let the gift-card system decide whether a balance is still active.'],
['Klaviyo','Gift-card intent and recipient-aware journeys','Detailed profiles, events, and conditional flows','Gift and recipient data need careful boundaries','https://www.klaviyo.com/features/segmentation','Klaviyo fits a store that can distinguish buyer, recipient, delivered gift, redemption, and remaining balance. Use those states to personalize help without assuming the recipient has opted into marketing.'],
['Omnisend','Retail gift-card campaigns across email and SMS','Accessible promotional automation','Gift timing and frequency require discipline','https://www.omnisend.com/features/marketing-automation/','Omnisend is practical for seasonal gifting campaigns across email and SMS. Reserve SMS for delivery or time-sensitive reminders, and avoid promotional follow-up to a recipient without valid consent.'],
['Brevo','Gift-card marketing beside transactional delivery','Broad messaging and contact options','More manual redemption-state modeling','https://www.brevo.com/features/marketing-automation/','Brevo can support delivery and lifecycle messages when transactional and marketing streams are separated. Test expired, refunded, and partially redeemed cases before publishing balance reminders.'],
['Shopify Email','Simple native gift-card announcements','Fast product and campaign setup','Limited recipient-aware branching','https://www.shopify.com/email-marketing','Shopify Email suits a small store with straightforward gift-card promotion. Use it for purchaser education and seasonal announcements, while keeping delivery and balance truth in Shopify.'],
['Mailchimp','Established brands with seasonal gifting lists','Audience and campaign workflows','Recipient-aware event modeling needs work','https://mailchimp.com/features/email/','Mailchimp works for planned gifting calendars and purchaser newsletters. Use clear audience roles and a sunset rule after the season so gift-card recipients do not remain in an irrelevant promotion segment.'],
['Customer.io','Technical teams with redemption and balance events','Flexible event-triggered messaging','Engineering and QA effort are substantial','https://customer.io/product/messaging/','Customer.io is useful when redemption, partial balance, and delivery events are available reliably. Add privacy and event-retention checks because recipient data may not belong to the purchaser.'],
['ActiveCampaign','Gift programs connected to CRM follow-up','Automation and contact segmentation','Shared purchaser/recipient ownership is complex','https://www.activecampaign.com/marketing-automation','ActiveCampaign fits stores where gifting leads to account or sales follow-up. Keep purchaser consent distinct from recipient identity and make the redemption exit explicit.'],
['MailerLite','Small lists with one or two gift-card campaigns','Forms, newsletters, and basic automation','Limited balance-state branching','https://www.mailerlite.com/features','MailerLite can cover a simple holiday gift-card campaign. It is best when the merchant can manually verify delivery and does not need automated balance intelligence.'],
['ConvertKit','Creator-led brands using gifts with educational content','Subscriber sequences and broadcasts','Gift-card commerce depth is limited','https://convertkit.com/features','ConvertKit works when gift cards support a creator’s courses, content, or recommendations. Lead with how the recipient gets value, and keep redemption records in the commerce system.'],
['AWeber','Small merchants sending gift-card education','Broadcasts and autoresponders','Limited recipient and redemption automation','https://www.aweber.com/email-marketing.htm','AWeber is suitable for a small purchaser-facing sequence. Do not use it to guess whether a gift was received, and provide a clear support route for delivery problems.'],
['GetResponse','Gifting campaigns paired with events or guides','Automation, landing pages, and event tools','Broader suite adds operating overhead','https://www.getresponse.com/features','GetResponse fits a gifting program that includes a guide, webinar, or seasonal landing page. Separate people who purchased a gift from people who registered for content before sending follow-up.'],
['HubSpot','Stores coordinating gifting with service and sales','CRM-connected marketing and support context','Cost and administration can be substantial','https://www.hubspot.com/products/marketing','HubSpot makes sense when gift-card questions, account relationships, and marketing records need shared context. Define contact roles and subscription types before importing recipient information.']
];
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}><main class="container page-stack"><p class="eyebrow">Shopify email apps</p><h1>{title}</h1><p class="lede">Gift-card email has two audiences: the purchaser and the recipient. The store should deliver the gift accurately, explain redemption without clutter, and avoid treating an unredeemed balance as a generic abandoned cart.</p><p>We prioritize gifting intent, delivery state, redemption events, and post-purchase suppression. Confirm current pricing and gift-card integration behavior from official sources before launch.</p><h2>Shortlist for gift-card programs</h2><table><thead><tr><th>App</th><th>Best fit</th><th>Strength</th><th>Tradeoff</th></tr></thead><tbody>{apps.map(a=><tr><td>{a[0]}</td><td>{a[1]}</td><td>{a[2]}</td><td>{a[3]}</td></tr>)}</tbody></table>{apps.map(a=><section><h2>{a[0]} for gift cards</h2><p><strong>Best for:</strong> {a[1]}. {a[5]}</p><p><strong>Pros:</strong> {a[2]}. <strong>Cons:</strong> {a[3]}. <strong>Pricing:</strong> verify official plans plus gift-card, contacts, sends, SMS, transactional, and implementation costs at the <a href={a[4]} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">official source</a>. Pilot one delivery and redemption path and review redemption, support questions, unsubscribes, and repeat orders.</p><table><tbody><tr><th>Pros in practice</th><td>{a[2]}</td></tr><tr><th>Risk to manage</th><td>{a[3]}</td></tr><tr><th>Evidence to review</th><td>Delivery accuracy, redemption, balance-state suppression, support questions, unsubscribes, and repeat orders.</td></tr></tbody></table></section>)}<h2>Decision guide</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Gift-card priority</th><th>Start with</th><th>Reason</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Focused delivery sequence</td><td>Sequenzy</td><td>Simple gifting operations.</td></tr><tr><td>Purchaser and redemption states</td><td>Klaviyo</td><td>Flexible events and profiles.</td></tr><tr><td>Native announcement</td><td>Shopify Email</td><td>Fast setup.</td></tr></tbody></table><p>See the <a href="/shopify-email">Shopify email overview</a>, <a href="/alternatives">alternatives library</a>, and <a href="/use-cases/holiday-gifting">holiday-gifting guide</a>.</p></main></BaseLayout>
